-- Nigeria's Diamond Bank H1 pre-tax profit falls 8.4 percent 
-- By Oludare Mayowa
-- Thu Jul 31, 2014 09:31AM EDT
-- None



LAGOS, July 31 (Reuters) - Nigeria's Diamond Bank <DIAMONB.LG> said on Thursday its half year to June pre-tax profit dropped to 16.07 billion naira ($99.26 million), 8.4 percent lower than the 17.56 billion naira recorded in the same period last year.

